text.tspan: Monthly average surface temperatures by year, Canada
The temperature of the air measured 2 meters above the ground, encompassing land, sea, and in-land water
Data source: Copernicus Climate Change Service (2024)
Note: The numbers 1 to 12 on the horizontal axis represent the months of the year, from 1 for January to 12 for December.
